{"tid":1301442,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"致聽日放榜的你","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T19:04:07.000Z","uid":104232,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35a3918c845024a62fce31928f66d01bca027239","tid":1301442,"uid":104232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"知道聽日放榜 <br />\n無論你係努力讀書個班<br />\n定係hea左六年個班 <br />\n聽日既結果都已成定局 <br />\n考得好既同學 固然開心啦 <br />\n準備直入A1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考得唔好既 都唔好灰心 <br />\n老套講句 條條大路通羅馬啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n六年過後既我睇返 <br />\n公開考試只係人生一少部分 <br />\n唔好因爲一個小小考試 否定自己能力 <br />\n十隻手指有長短 <br />\n<br />\n最後希望人人拎到offer 順利直入A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bba84791e80c080ef567c14a4e58e2d5368a448","tid":1301442,"uid":236222,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:02:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3485aba176b2b921a47e483f48ae0b9c627245ad","tid":1301442,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zJBpZ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zJBpZ9.png&h=a0f83e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報讀非本地高等及專業教育課程前，注意該課程是否經已辦理註冊或豁免註冊及相應的資歷架構級別。切勿一次繳交全部學費。要索取並保留學費收據。如有疑問，請到教育局網站查詢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://applications.edb.gov.hk/ncr/ncr.aspx?langno=2&amp;searchtype=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplications.edb.gov.hk%2Fncr%2Fncr.aspx%3Flangno%3D2%26searchtype%3D3&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=3467c428\" target=\"_blank\">https://applications.edb.gov.hk/ncr/ncr.aspx?langno=2&amp;searchtype=3</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局關心您。"}]}